The monthly wine tasting event was held at Mingles Liquor Emporium in Westlands on Friday evening showcasing the new range of wines from Ama La Vida.In attendance was Ama La Vida head of marketing Cleophas Liyayi, as well as invited wine lovers from across Nairobi.One of the event s highlights was the making of a unique wine cocktail putting a twist on the traditional method of drinking wine on its own.